<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        .head-title {
            border: 1px solid rgb(250, 229, 138);
            background: rgb(245, 239, 160);
            border-radius: 12px;
            color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
            padding-left: 42px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="head-title mt-3">Pizzazzio</h1>
        <h2>Hello {{name}}</h2>
        <h2>Thank you for trusting Pizzazzio! </h2>
        <p>We hope you'll love your meal from <strong>Pizzazzio</strong>.</p>
        <p>Eager for your feedback. <strong>Pizzazzio</strong> is always here to listen to your queries and your ordering experience.
            You can reach out to us by simply replying to this email.</p>
        <hr>
        <div class="card text-center" style="width: 58rem;">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">ORDER SUMMARY</h5>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <p>Order ID : {{foodID}}</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                        <p>Delivery Address : {{location}}, {{address}}</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <p>Pizza : {{foodName}}</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                        <p>For delivery details contact us at : +120999222111</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

<script>
    document.getElementById('qun').innerHTML = sessionStorage.getItem('qunt');
</script>